text: Bulan-Turgan () is a rural locality (a village) in Nadezhdinsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 60 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 57 km from Iglino, 8 km from Pyatiletka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Bulan-Turgan
